{"tid":933614,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵有創意朋友一齊創業","createTime":"2018-12-08T16:03:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-09T18:08:38.000Z","uid":223404,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1505996bdaf853775e3c772d67b784cd70f920bb","tid":933614,"uid":223404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T16:03:36.000Z","msg":"唔想打工打一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  身邊好多朋友都係淨係掛住番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔會諗下其他方法去賺錢！亦有好多人諗到又唔去做 結果就浪費左好多成功機會！<br />\n我想大家交流下 了解下 分享下諗法同意見！<br />\n話唔定 日後 我同你咖idea 可以成功殺出一條血路  我相信十個有九個人 靠自己係好難成事！ 但當搵到志同道合朋友一齊努力 效果可以好好   我相信 創意加上努力 可打出一片天！覺得自己有創意的朋友 我地一齊做個朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加telegram: <a href=\"http://t.me/Littlebabyaddsweet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FLittlebabyaddsweet&d=8SOQvrIox0hGW%2BDb74PY2%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=560b1e3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/Littlebabyaddsweet</a>"},{"pid":"5493b43f6b64d9ed5121f6276108a17debabef79","tid":933614,"uid":223404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T17:06:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1781da6955633a6205f78cd74ae4ac0a3ed27949","tid":933614,"uid":146535,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTim